                <h2 data-uuid="7f39e79d8c8f483ea879023d3b86eaca">The Great Compromise</h2>
                <p data-uuid="22157934b22f4a63926c08339ce95856">The Great Compromise outlined a plan for representation in
                    Congress that pleased both large and small states. </p>
            </article>
        </section>
